message:
Do you want to know a good trading day?
Here is the secret, make sure you set your trading view time to UTC -4. We have 5 trading days, so you count Monday, Tuesday and Wednesday as Day1, Day2 and Day3, then Wednesday, Thursday and Friday the same Day1, Day2 and Day3 respectively. Always volatility or big movement will occur on Day 3. And if Day3 volatility won't be there on the market expect it to happen the next day. No need to trade everyday wait on Day3 incorporate with your strategy and those are the days to make money in this market. Open your chart and backtest it and thank me later.
A good example is on this day volatility was supposed to be yesterday Wednesday which is Day3 and it the market never present it, and I waited for today
2418.48 is not a random level go to your daily chart and check it.
